data.description:
Cute and Cozy 2 bedroom 1 bath single family home. Kitchen has plenty of cabinet space, stove, refrigerator. Living Room has carpet, ceiling fan with lighting. Both bedrooms come with carpets and ceiling fans with lighting. Walk in pantry, walk in closet. Lanai is closed in for comfortable sitting areas. Spacious Backyard. Covered carport. This home is located within proximity of all major shopping facilities and easy access to the main roads and Hwy 75 North and South.
Rent includes Lawn Care and Pest Control

12 month minimum:
